[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6875,
        "end_time": 10353,
        "text": "Your favorite band is great\nat playing music,"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 10353,
        "end_time": 13474,
        "text": "but not so great at being organized."
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 13474,
        "end_time": 16264,
        "text": "They keep misplacing \ntheir instruments on tour,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 16264,
        "end_time": 18764,
        "text": "and it&#39;s driving their manager mad."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 18764,
        "end_time": 20574,
        "text": "On the day of the big concert,"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 20574,
        "end_time": 22884,
        "text": "the band wakes up \nto find themselves tied up"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 22884,
        "end_time": 26564,
        "text": "in a windowless, \nsoundproof practice room."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 26564,
        "end_time": 28804,
        "text": "Their manager explains what&#39;s happening."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 28804,
        "end_time": 32034,
        "text": "Outside, there are ten large boxes."
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 32034,
        "end_time": 34394,
        "text": "Each contains one of your instruments,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 34394,
        "end_time": 39214,
        "text": "but don&#39;t be fooled by the pictures -\nthey&#39;ve been randomly placed."
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 39214,
        "end_time": 42754,
        "text": "I&#39;m going to let you out one at a time."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 42754,
        "end_time": 46235,
        "text": "While you&#39;re outside, you can look\ninside any five boxes"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 46235,
        "end_time": 50234,
        "text": "before security\ntakes you back to the tour bus."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 50234,
        "end_time": 51903,
        "text": "You can&#39;t touch the instruments"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 51903,
        "end_time": 55804,
        "text": "or in any way communicate what you find\nto the others."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 55804,
        "end_time": 59574,
        "text": "No marking the boxes, shouting, nothing."
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 59574,
        "end_time": 62145,
        "text": "If each one of you \ncan find your own instrument,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 62145,
        "end_time": 64005,
        "text": "then you can play tonight."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 64005,
        "end_time": 67004,
        "text": "Otherwise, the label is dropping you."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 67004,
        "end_time": 70794,
        "text": "You have three minutes to think about it\nbefore we start."
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 70794,
        "end_time": 72334,
        "text": "The band is in despair."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 72334,
        "end_time": 76854,
        "text": "After all, each musician only has a 50%\nchance of finding their instrument"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 76854,
        "end_time": 79334,
        "text": "by picking five random boxes."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 79334,
        "end_time": 82650,
        "text": "And the chances that all ten will succeed\nare even lower -"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 82650,
        "end_time": 85774,
        "text": "just 1 in 1024."
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 85774,
        "end_time": 88464,
        "text": "But suddenly, the drummer comes up\nwith a valid strategy"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 88464,
        "end_time": 93044,
        "text": "that has a better than 35% chance\nof working."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 93044,
        "end_time": 95744,
        "text": "Can you figure out what it was?"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 95744,
        "end_time": 103765,
        "text": "Pause the video on the next screen\nif you want to figure it out for yourself!"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 103765,
        "end_time": 105214,
        "text": "Answer in: 3"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 105214,
        "end_time": 106215,
        "text": "Answer in: 2"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 106215,
        "end_time": 107645,
        "text": "Answer in: 1"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 107645,
        "end_time": 109285,
        "text": "Here&#39;s what the drummer said:"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 109285,
        "end_time": 113056,
        "text": "Everyone first open the box\nwith the picture of your instrument."
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 113056,
        "end_time": 115375,
        "text": "If your instrument is inside, you&#39;re done."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 115375,
        "end_time": 117555,
        "text": "Otherwise, look at whatever&#39;s in there,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 117555,
        "end_time": 120435,
        "text": "and then open the box \nwith that picture on it."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 120435,
        "end_time": 123505,
        "text": "Keep going that way until you find\nyour instrument."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 123505,
        "end_time": 125155,
        "text": "The bandmates are skeptical,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 125155,
        "end_time": 128225,
        "text": "but amazingly enough,\nthey all find what they need."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 128225,
        "end_time": 132096,
        "text": "And a few hours later, they&#39;re playing\nto thousands of adoring fans."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 132096,
        "end_time": 134655,
        "text": "So why did the drummer&#39;s strategy work?"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 134655,
        "end_time": 137285,
        "text": "Each musician follows a linked sequence"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 137285,
        "end_time": 140945,
        "text": "that starts with the box whose outside\nmatches their instrument"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 140945,
        "end_time": 145005,
        "text": "and ends with the box \nactually containing it."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 145005,
        "end_time": 148505,
        "text": "Note that if they kept going,\nthat would lead them back to the start,"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 148505,
        "end_time": 150106,
        "text": "so this is a loop."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 150106,
        "end_time": 152925,
        "text": "For example, if the boxes \nare arranged like so,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 152925,
        "end_time": 156034,
        "text": "the singer would open the first box\nto find the drums,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 156034,
        "end_time": 158265,
        "text": "go to the eighth box to find the bass,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 158265,
        "end_time": 161065,
        "text": "and find her microphone in the third box,"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 161065,
        "end_time": 163886,
        "text": "which would point back to the first."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 163886,
        "end_time": 166475,
        "text": "This works much better \nthan random guessing"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 166475,
        "end_time": 169824,
        "text": "because by starting with the box \nwith the picture of their instrument,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 169824,
        "end_time": 174435,
        "text": "each musician restricts their search to\nthe loop that contains their instrument,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 174435,
        "end_time": 177836,
        "text": "and there are decent odds, about 35%,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 177836,
        "end_time": 182277,
        "text": "that all of the loops \nwill be of length five or less."
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 182277,
        "end_time": 183925,
        "text": "How do we calculate those odds?"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 183925,
        "end_time": 187727,
        "text": "For the sake of simplicity, \nwe&#39;ll demonstrate with a simplified case,"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 187727,
        "end_time": 193486,
        "text": "four instruments and no more than \ntwo guesses allowed for each musician."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 193486,
        "end_time": 196327,
        "text": "Let&#39;s start by finding \nthe odds of failure,"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 196327,
        "end_time": 199677,
        "text": "the chance that someone will need\nto open three or four boxes"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 199677,
        "end_time": 201725,
        "text": "before they find their instrument."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 201725,
        "end_time": 204316,
        "text": "There are six distinct four-box loops."
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 204316,
        "end_time": 207457,
        "text": "One fun way to count them \nis to make a square,"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 207457,
        "end_time": 209626,
        "text": "put an instrument at each corner,"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 209626,
        "end_time": 211787,
        "text": "and draw the diagonals."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 211787,
        "end_time": 214617,
        "text": "See how many unique loops you can find,"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 214617,
        "end_time": 218107,
        "text": "and keep in mind that these two \nare considered the same,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 218107,
        "end_time": 220137,
        "text": "they just start at different points."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 220137,
        "end_time": 222398,
        "text": "These two, however, are different."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 222398,
        "end_time": 227098,
        "text": "We can visualize the eight distinct\nthree-box loops using triangles."
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 227098,
        "end_time": 229448,
        "text": "You&#39;ll find four possible triangles"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 229448,
        "end_time": 232017,
        "text": "depending on which instrument \nyou leave out,"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 232017,
        "end_time": 234948,
        "text": "and two distinct paths on each."
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 234948,
        "end_time": 238329,
        "text": "So of the 24 possible \ncombinations of boxes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 238329,
        "end_time": 240798,
        "text": "there are 14 that lead to faliure,"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 240798,
        "end_time": 243398,
        "text": "and ten that result in success."
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 243398,
        "end_time": 248468,
        "text": "That computational strategy works for any\neven number of musicians,"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 248468,
        "end_time": 249848,
        "text": "but if you want a shortcut,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 249848,
        "end_time": 253808,
        "text": "it generalizes to a handy equation."
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 253808,
        "end_time": 258107,
        "text": "Plug in ten musicians, \nand we get odds of about 35%."
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 258107,
        "end_time": 260428,
        "text": "What if there were 1,000 musicians?"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 260428,
        "end_time": 261798,
        "text": "1,000,000?"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 261798,
        "end_time": 266198,
        "text": "As n increases, \nthe odds approach about 30%."
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 266198,
        "end_time": 272228,
        "text": "Not a guarantee, but with a bit of\nmusician&#39;s luck, it&#39;s far from hopeless."
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 272228,
        "end_time": 275917,
        "text": "Hi everybody, if you liked this riddle,\ntry solving these two."
    }
]